{"subject_line": "Figma AI is now available", "preview_text": "Autocomplete designs, generate variations from text, and let AI handle the tedious layers.", "html_body": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n<title>Figma AI Launch</title>\n<meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n<meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1\">\n<meta name=\"color-scheme\" content=\"light dark\">\n<meta name=\"supported-color-schemes\" content=\"light dark\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">\n:root { color-scheme: light dark; supported-color-schemes: light dark; }\n@font-face {\n  font-family: 'Whyte';\n  font-style: normal;\n  font-weight: normal;\n  src: url(https://static.figma.com/uploads/9254519927cf4912e61627442d7ab7a5a9226581.woff) format('woff');\n  mso-font-alt: 'Arial';\n}\ntable, td { mso-table-lspace:0; mso-table-rspace:0; border-spacing:0; border:0; }\na { text-decoration:none; }\n@media screen and (max-width:639px) {\n  .w-100p { width:100% !important; }\n  .tflex { display:block !important; width:100% !important; }\n}\n@media (prefers-color-scheme:dark) {\n  .darkmode { background-color:#000000 !important; }\n  .light-img { display:none !important; }\n  .dark-img { display:block !important; width:auto !important; overflow:visible !important; max-height:inherit !important; max-width:inherit !important; visibility:inherit !important; }\n}\n[data-ogsc] .light-img { display:none !important; }\n[data-ogsc] .dark-img { display:block !important; width:auto !important; visibility:inherit !important; }\n[data-ogsc] .darkmode { background-color:#000000 !important; }\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"darkmode\" style=\"background:#FFFFFF;margin:0;padding:0;-webkit-text-size-adjust:100%;\">\n<div style=\"display:none;font-size:1px;color:#ffffff;line-height:1px;max-height:0;max-width:0;opacity:0;overflow:hidden;\">Autocomplete designs, generate variations from text, and let AI handle the tedious layers.                                        ‌‌‌‌‌‌‌‌‌‌‌‌‌‌‌‌‌‌‌‌</div>\n<table role=\"presentation\" width=\"100%\" style=\"background:#FFFFFF;min-width:320px;\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tr><td>\n<table role=\"presentation\" width=\"640\" align=\"center\" style=\"max-width:640px;margin:0 auto;\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tr><td align=\"left\" style=\"padding:24px 40px;\">\n  <a href=\"https://figma.com\" style=\"text-decoration:none;\">\n    <img class=\"light-img\" src=\"https://static.figma.com/uploads/f2c739b51898125e6ab81e67036787f570c03b0e\" width=\"110\" alt=\"Figma\" style=\"width:110px;max-width:110px;border:0;\" />\n  </a>\n  <div class=\"dark-img\" style=\"display:none;overflow:hidden;max-height:0;max-width:0;visibility:hidden;\">\n    <a href=\"https://figma.com\"><img src=\"https://static.figma.com/uploads/53280c3b3748be75104b3f237318ba3036b959b7\" width=\"110\" alt=\"Figma\" style=\"width:110px;border:0;\" /></a>\n  </div>\n</td></tr></table><table role=\"presentation\" width=\"640\" align=\"center\" style=\"max-width:640px;margin:0 auto;\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tr><td align=\"center\" style=\"padding:0 0 24px;\">\n  <a href=\"https://figma.com/ai\"><img src=\"https://static.figma.com/uploads/03ac25c18fff770974c2f56dbf6416ea90c5eb5e\" width=\"640\" alt=\"Your design process, accelerated\" style=\"width:640px;max-width:100%;border:0;display:block;\" /></a>\n</td></tr></table><table role=\"presentation\" width=\"640\" align=\"center\" style=\"max-width:640px;margin:0 auto;\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tr><td style=\"padding:0 40px;\">\n<p style=\"font-size:26px;line-height:30px;font-family:'Whyte', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;color:#000000;font-weight:bold;text-align:center;margin:0;padding:20px 0 30px;\">Your design process, accelerated</p>\n</td></tr></table><table role=\"presentation\" width=\"640\" align=\"center\" style=\"max-width:640px;margin:0 auto;\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tr><td style=\"padding:0 40px;\">\n<p style=\"font-size:20px;line-height:28px;font-family:'Whyte', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;color:#000000;text-align:center;margin:0;padding:0 0 20px;\">After 3 months of beta with overwhelmingly positive feedback, Figma AI is ready for everyone. Autocomplete your designs, generate variations from text prompts, and let AI handle the tedious layers so you can focus on the creative work.</p>\n</td></tr></table><table role=\"presentation\" width=\"640\" align=\"center\" style=\"max-width:640px;margin:0 auto;background:#FFFFFF;\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tr><td style=\"padding:30px 40px 60px;\">\n<table role=\"presentation\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" align=\"center\">\n  <tr><td align=\"center\" style=\"background-color:#5551FF;border:5px solid #5551FF;border-radius:8px;font-family:'Whyte', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:20px;font-weight:bold;\">\n    <a href=\"https://figma.com/ai\" style=\"padding:12px 27px;color:#FFFFFF;text-decoration:none;display:block;\">Try Figma AI</a>\n  </td></tr></table>\n</td></tr></table><table role=\"presentation\" width=\"640\" align=\"center\" style=\"max-width:640px;margin:0 auto;\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tr><td style=\"padding:0 40px 50px;\">\n<table role=\"presentation\" width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tr>\n  <td valign=\"top\" width=\"150\" style=\"padding:0;\">\n    <a href=\"https://figma.com/ai\"><img src=\"https://static.figma.com/uploads/c945b793ff6a1f4d7fc5e3f6cb28967aa5a3eb5e\" width=\"150\" alt=\"Figma AI autocomplete example\" style=\"width:150px;max-width:150px;border:0;\" /></a>\n  </td>\n  <td valign=\"middle\" style=\"padding:0 0 0 24px;font-family:'Whyte', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">\n    <p style=\"font-size:22px;line-height:28px;font-weight:bold;color:#000000;margin:0;\">Autocomplete designs</p>\n    <p style=\"font-size:18px;line-height:22px;color:#000000;margin:10px 0 0;\">Figma AI predicts and completes your design patterns, saving you time on repetitive tasks.</p>\n    <p style=\"font-size:18px;line-height:21px;margin:10px 0 0;\">\n      <a href=\"https://figma.com/ai\" style=\"color:#5551FF;font-weight:bold;text-decoration:none;\">Learn more →</a>\n    </p>\n  </td>\n</tr></table>\n</td></tr></table><table role=\"presentation\" width=\"640\" align=\"center\" style=\"max-width:640px;margin:0 auto;\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tr><td style=\"padding:0 40px 50px;\">\n<table role=\"presentation\" width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tr>\n  <td valign=\"top\" width=\"150\" style=\"padding:0;\">\n    <a href=\"https://figma.com/ai\"><img src=\"https://static.figma.com/uploads/c945b793ff6a1f4d7fc5e3f6cb28967aa5a3eb5e\" width=\"150\" alt=\"Figma AI text-to-design example\" style=\"width:150px;max-width:150px;border:0;\" /></a>\n  </td>\n  <td valign=\"middle\" style=\"padding:0 0 0 24px;font-family:'Whyte', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">\n    <p style=\"font-size:22px;line-height:28px;font-weight:bold;color:#000000;margin:0;\">Generate variations from text</p>\n    <p style=\"font-size:18px;line-height:22px;color:#000000;margin:10px 0 0;\">Describe what you need in plain language and watch Figma AI create multiple design options instantly.</p>\n    <p style=\"font-size:18px;line-height:21px;margin:10px 0 0;\">\n      <a href=\"https://figma.com/ai\" style=\"color:#5551FF;font-weight:bold;text-decoration:none;\">Learn more →</a>\n    </p>\n  </td>\n</tr></table>\n</td></tr></table><table role=\"presentation\" width=\"640\" align=\"center\" style=\"max-width:640px;margin:0 auto;\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tr><td style=\"padding:0 40px 50px;\">\n<table role=\"presentation\" width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tr>\n  <td valign=\"top\" width=\"150\" style=\"padding:0;\">\n    <a href=\"https://figma.com/ai\"><img src=\"https://static.figma.com/uploads/726c6143248e475d620cde1e8da7c39a1e0ce76e\" width=\"150\" alt=\"Figma AI layer management example\" style=\"width:150px;max-width:150px;border:0;\" /></a>\n  </td>\n  <td valign=\"middle\" style=\"padding:0 0 0 24px;font-family:'Whyte', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">\n    <p style=\"font-size:22px;line-height:28px;font-weight:bold;color:#000000;margin:0;\">Focus on creative work</p>\n    <p style=\"font-size:18px;line-height:22px;color:#000000;margin:10px 0 0;\">Let AI handle layer organization, spacing adjustments, and other tedious details while you shape the big picture.</p>\n    <p style=\"font-size:18px;line-height:21px;margin:10px 0 0;\">\n      <a href=\"https://figma.com/ai\" style=\"color:#5551FF;font-weight:bold;text-decoration:none;\">Learn more →</a>\n    </p>\n  </td>\n</tr></table>\n</td></tr></table><table role=\"presentation\" width=\"640\" align=\"center\" style=\"max-width:640px;margin:0 auto;background:#FFFFFF;\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tr><td style=\"padding:30px 40px 60px;\">\n<table role=\"presentation\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" align=\"center\">\n  <tr><td align=\"center\" style=\"background-color:#5551FF;border:5px solid #5551FF;border-radius:8px;font-family:'Whyte', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:20px;font-weight:bold;\">\n    <a href=\"https://figma.com/ai\" style=\"padding:12px 27px;color:#FFFFFF;text-decoration:none;display:block;\">Try Figma AI</a>\n  </td></tr></table>\n</td></tr></table><table role=\"presentation\" width=\"640\" align=\"center\" style=\"max-width:640px;margin:0 auto;border-top:1px solid #DEDEDE;background:#FFFFFF;\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tr><td style=\"padding:35px 40px 46px;\" align=\"center\">\n  <table role=\"presentation\" width=\"410\" align=\"center\" style=\"max-width:410px;margin:0 auto;\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n  <tr><td align=\"center\" style=\"padding:15px 0 32px;font-size:14px;line-height:20px;font-family:'Whyte', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;color:#a5a5a5;\">\n    Figma is a design platform for teams who build products together. Born on the Web, Figma helps the entire product team create, test, and ship better designs, faster.\n  </td></tr>\n  <tr><td style=\"padding:0 0 32px;\"><table role=\"presentation\" align=\"center\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\"><tr><td class=\"active-i\" style=\"line-height:1px;font-size:1px;\"><a href=\"https://figma.com\"><img src=\"https://static.figma.com/uploads/a9c9c230c0a9395f5eaa1c4acb6ee89d13782987\" width=\"30\" alt=\"Figma\" style=\"width:30px;border:0;\" /></a></td><td width=\"30\" style=\"font-size:1px;line-height:1px;\"></td><td class=\"active-i\" style=\"line-height:1px;font-size:1px;\"><a href=\"https://twitter.com/figma\"><img src=\"https://static.figma.com/uploads/5bb05074a2c9507b003979dd88c1bb852fb875b7\" width=\"30\" alt=\"Twitter\" style=\"width:30px;border:0;\" /></a></td><td width=\"30\" style=\"font-size:1px;line-height:1px;\"></td><td class=\"active-i\" style=\"line-height:1px;font-size:1px;\"><a href=\"https://instagram.com/figma\"><img src=\"https://static.figma.com/uploads/9dc8394d92432c5cd16ab9e61ee574da29434ec8\" width=\"30\" alt=\"Instagram\" style=\"width:30px;border:0;\" /></a></td><td width=\"30\" style=\"font-size:1px;line-height:1px;\"></td><td class=\"active-i\" style=\"line-height:1px;font-size:1px;\"><a href=\"https://youtube.com/figmadesign\"><img src=\"https://static.figma.com/uploads/4db5401f0db17df56b55b663da4ec93b18f2d707\" width=\"30\" alt=\"YouTube\" style=\"width:30px;border:0;\" /></a></td><td width=\"30\" style=\"font-size:1px;line-height:1px;\"></td><td class=\"active-i\" style=\"line-height:1px;font-size:1px;\"><a href=\"https://linkedin.com/company/figma\"><img src=\"https://static.figma.com/uploads/02676955b299a6571870721434fcc596c6b8de56\" width=\"30\" alt=\"LinkedIn\" style=\"width:30px;border:0;\" /></a></td></tr></table></td></tr>\n  <tr><td align=\"center\" style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:18px;font-family:'Whyte', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;color:#B2B2B2;padding-bottom:8px;\">\n    Figma, Inc. · 760 Market St · San Francisco, CA 94102\n  </td></tr>\n  <tr><td align=\"center\" style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:18px;font-family:'Whyte', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;color:#B2B2B2;\">\n    <a href=\"*|UNSUBSCRIBE|*\" style=\"color:#B2B2B2;text-decoration:underline;\">Unsubscribe</a>\n  </td></tr>\n  </table>\n</td></tr></table>\n</td></tr></table>\n</body>\n</html>", "plain_text": "Figma AI is now available. Autocomplete your designs, generate variations from text prompts, and let AI handle the tedious layers so you can focus on the creative work. After 3 months of beta with overwhelmingly positive feedback, we're excited to bring AI to your workflow.\n\nLearn more and get started: https://figma.com/ai\n\nFigma is a design platform for teams who build products together. Follow us on Twitter, Instagram, YouTube, and LinkedIn. Figma, Inc. · 760 Market St · San Francisco, CA 94102. Unsubscribe: *|UNSUBSCRIBE|*", "template_used": "product_launch", "confidence_score": 5, "provider": "cached", "sync": {"success": true, "provider": "customer.io (cached)", "detail": "Pre-generated demo result."}}